{"tid":765139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殺手鐧未出】美商務部長：關稅加碼 對中國非「災難性」","createTime":"2018-08-02T13:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T14:02:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1ea79639802d6dc147b353364e9fa70c2a175b","tid":765139,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533213907_a4ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533213907_a4ab.jpg&h=9152fa97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）周四表示，美國威脅向接近五成的中國進口貨品徵收關稅加碼至25%，對中國不會帶來「災難」，影響只是有限。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯接受美國霍士新聞訪問時形「這（徵稅）並非災難性」，他解釋美國向2,000億美元（1.56萬億港元）的貨品徵收25%關稅，估計每年金額僅為500億美元（3,900億港元），只佔中國生產總值不足百分之一。羅斯又稱，美方已豁免了向1,000項中國製產品徵收關稅。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普今年5月已下令引用美國《1962年貿易擴展法》第232條款，調查進口汽車會否損害國家安全，至今調查仍然繼續。雖然美國初步同意不向歐洲車徵收關稅，但羅斯表示，美方仍計劃完成調查，但只會在與歐洲談判失敗後，才會向歐洲車徵收關稅。"},{"pid":"2ab92279de0058b88e6fe18e912eb1d282ce8cab","tid":765139,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔怪得中國唔驚"},{"pid":"cd14a13a2400660fba45a75b96262a04f8451327","tid":765139,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔能系仲念住支爆"},{"pid":"a64acbb47817b17ee69469b5dc1430c80bbca570","tid":765139,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/